著眼睛望著媽媽和那個男人，決定以沉默代表自己最後的人性尊嚴。媽媽大怒並嚴厲地說： 「快叫爸爸！」 <br />\n<br />\nLucas和媽媽僵持著。 <br />\n<br />\n媽媽急了、也火了，伸出右手打了Lucas一巴掌，並且大吼：「快叫爸爸！你站在那裡發什麼發呆啊。」 <br />\n<br />\nLucas頓時傻了，沒想到媽媽竟會為了一個男人而打他，Lucas難過的哭了出來，說：「爸&hellip;爸&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\n<br />\n媽媽哭笑不得地說：「你白癡啊~~~你這樣叫爸爸，他怎聽到嗎？ 人家來修電腦，你趕快到房裡去叫爸爸，帶他上樓 。」"},{"pid":"82ce8d1e9efb832e579c6196a1f8e71e7c137cf6","tid":2345180,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"257b804a98ac480297e87e58843ceeb3d1588229","tid":2345180,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe79ddab7a4d51fe62a9971fc336dfa28b873b6","tid":2345180,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢唱live唔係一向都係咁?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"係 出道果陣已經係<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cOWvVq7oaDY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcOWvVq7oaDY&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e3db4b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cOWvVq7oaDY</a><br />\n<br />\n已經係咁聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"啲人話佢嗰時好似上咗電先上去"},{"pid":"4504c7d47fac38c344b8212c3ca6295c7dfb3883","tid":2345180,"uid":128369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"209b65494bd9d26bc5d30551c5cb01cd963df94e","tid":2345180,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe79ddab7a4d51fe62a9971fc336dfa28b873b6","tid":2345180,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢唱live唔係一向都係咁?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"佢本來就唔係唱得好<br />\n咁啱嗰個年代出名就有得出碟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"陳少寶都話張柏芝唱歌唔係為做音樂只係為搵錢"},{"pid":"496c14758e0cb622a5e30c603ba498ea34f0b71e","tid":2345180,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"好心啦點會搵佢唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}